snippet.title: 5 October 2023 Product Ownership and Lean Product Development Webinar
snippet.description:

Join us for an enlightening 18-minute journey with two of the industry's leading experts, Dr. Joanna P≈Çaskonka and Martin Hinshelwood, as they unravel the intricacies of Product Ownership and Lean Product Development.

üîç What to Expect? What to Expect?
